  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project Title: Emergency Response to meet the immediate food and other basic needs of people affected by Cyclone Amphan in the South-West Areas of Bangladesh.
Duration: 1 Jun 2020 to 30 Sep 2020
Summary: The purpose of this action is to meet the emergency needs of cyclone Amphan affected women and
men in the worst affected Satkhira and Khulna districts. The action focuses on WASH, emergency shelter NFI, food security &amp; livelihood support.</narrative>
